  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuditLoggingComponent, OMRSMetadataCollectionManager
    public class ReadOnlyOMRSRepositoryConnector
extends InMemoryOMRSRepositoryConnector
    The ReadOnlyOMRSRepositoryConnector is a connector to a local in memory repository. It is used for test, small scale fixed or temporary repositories where the initial content comes from open metadata archives and other members of connected open metadata repository cohorts.
